message.content:
A small L‐shaped kitchen with black lower and upper cabinets runs along two adjoining walls. A pale marble‐look countertop spans underneath the cabinets, interrupted in one corner by a metallic sink (under a wooden‐framed window) and a cooktop with a small pot on it. Above the cooktop hangs a wooden range hood. On the countertop near the cooktop, a bright orange mug sits beside a cereal box labeled “Chucky” and a jar of jam. Moving along the countertop toward the fridge, there is another cereal box labeled “Rice Bubbles,” a stack of white plates, a box of strawberry Jell‐O, and a cylindrical container of “Alpen Salt,” all arranged side by side. The white fridge stands just to the right of these cabinets, against a slight protruding wall.

Past the fridge, the space opens into a dining area. A rectangular wooden table occupies the center, surrounded by four white upholstered chairs. On the table, a large plastic water bottle stands inside a white fruit bowl (the bowl contains several citrus fruits around the bottle). Next to it, a black box of shortbread rests near a clear pitcher and a single wine glass. A wooden door is on one side of the dining area, and an overhead pendant light hangs above the table. The entire floor is laid with a brown parquet pattern.
